29I.F.summary: ITAB Shop Concept AB (publ) develops, manufactures, sells, and installs shop fitting concepts for retail chain stores. It offers various COVID-19 solutions, such as automated people counting, vitual queue, plexiglas shields for pharmacies and grocery stores, mini-mart pop-up shops, and hygiene stations, as well as temporary checkout pods; entrance and exit systems, such as automatic gates, gate arms, ADS direction alarms, mechanical gates, in queue merchandising products, call forward queue systems, screen walls, and shop accessories; and shop fittings. The company also provides lighting products, including track lights and systems, downlights and recessed lights, linear lights, LED panels, uplights, surface-mounted and pendant lighting products, strips and coils, exterior and fuel lighting products, and emergency lighting solutions, as well as wireless lighting, sound, and images system; manned and self-checkout, as well as drug storage solutions for pharmacies and hospitals. In addition, it offers service and maintenance for its products. It has operations in the United Kingdom, Sweden, Norway, Germany, Denmark, the United States, Finland, Italy, France, the Netherlands, Poland, Czech Republic, Argentina, Lithunia, Spain, Russia, and internationally. PRIC-B.ST.summary: Pricer AB (publ) manufactures and sells electronic shelf label systems in Sweden, France, Netherlands, the United States, Norway, and internationally. The company offers digital pricing tags, such as graphic and segment price tags; and attachments. It provides Pricer Plaza, a cloud-based platform for the complete scalable management, monitoring, and integration of a digital in-store system; SmartPOSTER, a solution to display promotions, fruit and veg, delicatessen, price, fish or dairy products, etc.; and The Pricer platform, an in-store digital platform. The company markets and sells its products through direct sales and resellers. It serves customers primarily in grocery retail, DIY, electronics chains, and the pharmacy industry. Pricer AB (publ) was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
